title: Enthusiasm, but also some uncertainty, at Sanders’s last scheduled public event before Tuesday’s debate
text: BOULDER, Colo. — Bernie Sanders was greeted by another large, boisterous crowd — this one estimated at 9,000 people — as he held what will likely be his final public event before Tuesday’s high-profile Democratic debate.
